title: Was It Won Or Lost?
description:
Pablo Torre, Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth debate if the bigger story from last night was Patrick Mahomes' clutch performance or Brandon Staley being too aggressive and Trevor Lawrence's comments about Urban Meyer’s departure.
